## 1. INTERPRETIVE FRAMEWORK

### Historicist/Adventist Hermeneutic

This analysis follows the historicist method of prophetic interpretation, which understands Bible prophecy as unfolding progressively through history from the time of the prophet to the end of time. This is in contrast to preterism (all fulfilled in the past) or futurism (all to be fulfilled in a brief future period).

**Core principle: Let the Bible interpret itself.**

> "To the law and to the testimony: if they speak not according to this word, it is because there is no light in them." — **Isaiah 8:20**

---

